OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,6,Fmore unsettled into the weekend with
OL,7,Fmore showers and possible thundery
OL,8,Foutbreaks. Staying warm for the coming
OL,9,Fdays.
